  29 May 2003; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> kmerlin-1.3_beta3.ebuild:
  Added ~sparc to keywords.

  06 Apr 2003; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> kmerlin-1.3_beta3.ebuild :
  
  Mark as x86 stable.

*kmerlin-1.3_beta3 (3 Mar 2003) Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> kmerlin-1.3_beta3.ebuild :

  New version with added patch to fix compilation (bug #14285);
  also added dep on kde 3.1 (3.0 doesn't work).

  30 Jan 2003; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> ChangeLog  :

  Change ebuilds to use kde_src_unpack() instead of base_src_unpack(). This
  does not affect in any way the compiled output, or any ebuild not suffering
  rfom the 'languageChange undeclared' bug, which it fixes.

*kmerlin-1.3_beta2 (12 Jan 2003)

  12 Jan 2003; Hannes Mehnert <hannes@gentoo.org> kmerlin-1.3_beta2.ebuild:
  version bump

  14 Dec 2002; Hannes Mehnert <hannes@gentoo.org> kmerlin-1.2.ebuild:
  removed some cpp and h files (which should be generated by uic).
  This solves bug #11907, thanks to throstur@bylur.net (Throstur Svanbergsson)
  for submission

*kmerlin-1.2 (01 Aug 2002)

  01 Aug 2002; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> ChangeLog  :

  New upstream version.

*kmerlin-1.0-r1 (31 May 2002)

  31 May 2002; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> changelog:
  
  Force usage of autoconf-2.1x to fix bug #3261.

*kmerlin-1.0 (30 April 2002)

  30 April 2002; Bart Verwilst <verwilst@gentoo.org> ebuild :

  Version update, bugfix release.

*kmerlin-0.3.3 (11 Mar 2002)

  11 Mar 2002; Guido Bakker <guidob@gentoo.org> ebuild :

  Version update, bugfix release.

*kmerlin-0.3.1 (1 Feb 2002)

  1 Feb 2002; G.Bevin <gbevin@gentoo.org> ChangeLog :
  
  Added initial ChangeLog which should be updated whenever the package is
  updated in any way. This changelog is targetted to users. This means that the
  comments should well explained and written in clean English. The details about
  writing correct changelogs are explained in the skel.ChangeLog file which you
  can find in the root directory of the portage repository.
